Edward Faye PARKS, Petitioner,
v.
Bruno STOLC, Warden, et al. No. 18-9528 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States *320Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
